        "description": "<p>This plugin allows you to send comment moderation notifications to different email addresses based on post language. Requires the WMPL plugin.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Download the plugin .zip archive and unpack it. </li>\n<li>Locate the plugin file and upload to your website Plugins folder.</li>\n<li>Log into WordPress and activate the plugin. </li>\n<li>Once the plugin is activated, go to <code>Settings &gt; Discussion</code> and add an email address for each of your site&#8217;s languages.</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "faq": "\n<h4>Do I need to add an email address for each language?</h4>\n<p>\n<p>No, where no email is specified, notifications will default to the main admin address.</p>\n</p>\n\n",
